train_xpos<-train_xpos %>%
    mutate("id" = seq.int(nrow(train_xpos)))%>%
    melt(id.vars = c("id","class"),value.name="X")

Moreover, it may become be impossible to differentiate gestures' classes with reduced dimension view by using first component values after applying pca for each class separately.
